1. *Pritisak* na svetskom nivou je sve veći. (The pressure on a global level is increasing.) 
2. *Pritisak* na političare je veliki. (The pressure on politicians is high.) 
3. *Pritišću* ga da odluči. (They are pressuring him to make a decision.) 
4. Ne sme da se podvrgne *pritisci* okoline. (He must not succumb to the pressure of the environment.) 
5. Pokušaji da se izdejstvuje *pritisak* su pogrešni. (Attempts to exert pressure are wrong.)